<Link id="l00285" /><CodeLine lineNumber="285"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// Avoid realigning functions that explicitly do not want to be realigned.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00286" /><CodeLine lineNumber="286"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// Normally, we should report an error when a function should be dynamically</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00287" /><CodeLine lineNumber="287"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// realigned but also has the attribute no-realign-stack. Unfortunately,</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
